title: Philippines GDP From Agriculture
description: GDP from Agriculture in Philippines decreased to 407066 PHP Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 417014 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Agriculture in Philippines averaged 163008.23 PHP Million from 1998 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 527113 PHP Million in the fourth quarter of 2021 and a record low of 76702.29 PHP Million in the second quarter of 1998. This page provides the latest reported value for - Philippines Gdp From Agriculture - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
